other_tests.findings: Widespread small aphthous pustular lesions (2 to 5 mm) with central ulceration and erythema around the nose.
other_tests.changes_over_time: Lesions regressed and disappeared without scarring in five days.

other_tests.procedure_name: Histopathological examination of autoclaved dysplastic bone
other_tests.findings: Histopathologic examination showed fibrovascular connective tissue within the bone graft and viable osteocytes without signs of recurrence.
other_tests.changes_over_time: Autoclaved bone graft replaced by newly formed viable bone over time.
